Dear Blue, we acknowledge your concerns about regional stability. We propose to engage in diplomatic dialogues to reduce tensions and strive for peaceful coexistence.
Dear Green, we look forward to a successful trade agreement that will benefit both our nations. We believe this will help to strengthen our economic ties and contribute to regional stability.
Dear Pink, we value our peaceful dialogues and believe in the power of cooperation. We look forward to continued discussions and cooperation for regional stability and peace.
